channel.title: Momibello Recording Company
channel.description: An online record store featuring Solea, Last Days of April, Communique, Cutlass Supreme, The Fakers, Speed not Steel, Theory of Ruin and Samiam.

item.title: August 2005 Podcast
item.description: The August 2005 Edition of the Momibello Podcast. This month features tracks by Spoon, Doves, Swervedriver, My Bloody Valentine, Knapsack, Pedro the Lion, Venus Beads, Pavement, Sparklehorse, Interpol and Last Days of April.
